You must be one of Halgok's men... Please take the prisoner to Halgok at once, for Malthar is growing quite antsy...
<StartAction>[This guard, one of the members of the Nightcrawler gang which abducted Tarin, looks towards you as you approach.]</Start>
Speak with Malthar if you have business here...
You must be from Halgok's crew... Malthar has been expecting you. You may pass.
Halt! What is your business?
<StartAction>[The guard quickly reaches for his blade.]</Start> Sound the alarm! Intruders! Attack!
<StartAction>[The guard looks annoyed by your response.]</Start> This is where Malthar is keeping his prized prisoner until the boat arrives. I would think you would know this...
Now get on out of here, <lad/lass>! I have no more time for foolish questions!
<StartAction>[The guard looks at you in suspicion.]</Start> Why was I not informed of this? Besides... I haven't seen you around here before...
<StartCheck>[Failure]</Start> I was not informed of your arrival, so I cannot let you pass. You'll need to speak with Malthar to get permission for entering this cell...
<StartAction>[Success]</Start> I suppose you seem truthful enough. Very well. Be sure not to be too rough with the prisoner. Malthar wants him in good condition when we deliver him to Pharos.
<StartAction>[The guard steps aside, motioning for you to enter through the door.]</Start>
<StartAction>[The guard looks towards you with glazed eyes.]</Start> As you wish... You may pass...
Who you be? Why you approach? What you want?
<StartCheck>[Failure]</Start> Me not believe you! You go now, before you gets hurt!
<StartAction>[Success]</Start> Alright... you pass through. <StartAction>[The guard steps out of the way, unlocking the door and allowing you entry.]</Start>
Alright... you pass through. <StartAction>[The guard steps out of the way, unlocking the door and allowing you entry.]</Start>
<StartAction>[With the door now open, you see a chance to strike at the guard before he can react. Do you wish to do so?]</Start>
What you waitin' for? Go on through!
<StartAction>[With a quick swing of your weapon, the guard falls to the ground in a dead slump...]</Start>
This be Nightcrawler business. If you know what's good for you, you'd best go topside...
Why not take a seat and join us for a bit, <lad/lass>?
We're tryin' to enjoy a drink here, so why don't you find someone else to bother, <lad/lass>...

I have come to claim your life, rogue!
What's behind this cell?
<StartAction>[Leave.]</Start>
<StartAction>[Wisdom]</Start> Our mutual friend Halgok sent me.
<StartAction>[Intelligence]</Start> Halgok sent me to pick up the prisoner.
Er... yes, well... Oh, forget it! Prepare to die!
<StartAction>[Persuade]</Start> I just joined.
Forget it... Prepare to die, scum!
Very well. I'll do that.
<StartAction>[Charisma]</Start> Step aside and open this door...
<StartAction>[Persuade]</Start> I must speak with Malthar at once!
<StartAction>[Leave.]</Start>
I have a better idea... Prepare to die, rogue!
<StartAction>[Wisdom]</Start> Our mutual friend Halgok sent me.
<StartAction>[Intelligence]</Start> Halgok sent me to pick up the prisoner.
<StartAction>[Charisma]</Start> You will allow me to pass...
<StartAction>[No.]</Start>
<StartAction>[Walk through the open door.]</Start>
<StartAction>[Yes.]</Start>
